  "text": "Google Pixel Watch 2 $130 $250 Save $120 Case Material Aluminum Case size 41mm Colors Matte Black; Polished Silver; Champagne Gold Display 1.2\" 450 x 450 AMOLED CPU Qualcomm Snapdragon W5 with Cortex M33 co-processor The Pixel Watch 2 effectively strikes the sweet spot in terms of features, functionality, and price. You get a sleek design that never goes out of style, and it's packed with fantastic health and fitness tracking features. The best part is that it's now down to a record low price at just $130. Don't bother looking at other smartwatches if you want something stylish, feature-packed, and more importantly affordable. While there are plenty of great deals on smartwatches for Prime Day, we think this Pixel Watch 2 for $130 hits the sweet spot. This is the best price that we've seen on this watch, with a discount that knocks nearly 50% off its current retail price. What's great about the Pixel Watch 2? Google really got a lot of things right with the Pixel Watch 2, delivering an experience that many people were looking for when the brand released its first smartwatch. While not much changed when it came to the looks, the Pixel Watch 2 really made some big changes when it came to battery life, delivering true all-day use without any compromises. You also get excellent health and fitness tracking, along with access to a wide variety of apps for wearables thanks to Wear OS. The good news is that Google will continue to support this watch with updates, delivering fresh new features, and offering support until October 2026. When it comes to hardware, the Pixel Watch 2 comes in just one size, with the 41mm model featuring a 1.2-inch AMOLED screen that can reach up to 1,000 nits of brightness. You also get a Qualcomm Snapdragon W5 processor that's paired with 2GB of RAM and 32GB of internal storage. There are also a wealth of different sensors that can track your health and fitness metrics, and it also has an IP68 rating that protects it against dust and moisture. You really can't go wrong with the Pixel Watch 2. It offers plenty of bang for your buck, especially at this newly discounted price, which makes it a no-brainer if you've been looking for a new smartwatch. Get it now while you still can, or just in case the Pixel Watch 2 isn't to your liking, you can check out some other smartwatch deals we've covered during Prime Day.",
